videos.headline: Miss State's Willie Gay Jr. scores on 52-yard pick-6
videos.description: Willie Gay Jr. picks off Sawyer Smith's pass and brings it back 52 yards to the house for the touchdown.

videos.headline: MSU's Kylin Hill goes up and over for the score
